long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Troyan Launch Tab is a Chrome extension that replaces the New Tab page with a more functional and informative one, which includes daily weather features and organizes your bookmarks in a convenient manner for a streamlined display.


Click "Add to Chrome" to install, change your New Tab with Microsoft Bing results, and consent to the TOU and Privacy Policy. For further details, please visit:


Privacy Policy: https://troyanlaunchtabapp.com/questions/ext_privacy.html
Terms of Use: https://troyanlaunchtabapp.com/questions/ext_terms.html
About: https://troyanlaunchtabapp.com/questions/ext_about.html
Contact: https://troyanlaunchtabapp.com/questions/ext_contact.html
